    "prompt": "Draw a toilet:\n\nArt Style Introduction: Minimalist 3D Illustration\nVisual Elements\nShape Language: Rounded edges, smooth and soft forms, using simplified geometric shapes.\nColors: Primary colors: Soft beige, light gray, warm orange. Accent color: Warm orange for focal elements. Light and shadow treatment: Soft gradients, smooth transitions, avoiding strong shadows and highlights.\nLighting: Type: Soft, diffused lighting. Light direction: From above, slightly to the right. Shadow style: Subtle and diffused, no sharp or high-contrast shadows.\nMaterials: Surface texture: Matte, smooth surfaces with subtle tonal variations. Reflectivity: Low or none, avoiding obvious glossiness.\nComposition: Object presentation: Single, centered object with ample negative space around it. Perspective: Slightly tilted angle, showing moderate three-dimensionality without noticeable depth of field effects. Background: Solid color, low saturation, harmonious with the subject without distracting from it.\nTypography: Font style: Minimalist, sans-serif font. Text position: Lower left corner, small and understated. Font color: Gray, low contrast with the background.\nRendering Style: Technique: 3D rendering with a simplified low-poly style. Detail level: Medium detail, focusing on shape and color, avoiding complex textures and details.",
