    "prompt": "An ultra-realistic 3D rendered scene recreating Natasha's character design from the 2008 game \"Command & Conquer: Red Alert 3,\" faithfully following the original model. The scene is set in a dimly lit, cluttered 2008-era bedroom, where the character is sitting on the carpet, facing an old-fashioned TV playing \"Command & Conquer: Red Alert 3\" with a game controller nearby.\n\nThe entire room is filled with 2008-era nostalgic atmosphere: snack wrappers, soda cans, posters, and tangled wires. Natasha Volkova is captured in the moment of turning her head, looking back at the camera, with a hint of innocent smile on her iconic ethereally beautiful face. Her upper body is slightly twisted, with natural dynamics, as if reacting to being startled by a camera flash.\n\nThe flash slightly overexposes her face and clothes, making her silhouette stand out more prominently in the dim room. The entire photo looks raw and natural, with strong chiaroscuro casting deep shadows behind her, the image full of tactile quality, carrying an authentic 2008 film snapshot analog texture.",
