    "prompt": "Create an RPG collectible-style digital character card. The character is set as a {Programmer}, standing confidently with tools or symbols related to their profession. Rendered in 3D cartoon style with soft lighting, showcasing a distinctive personality. Add skill bars or attribute values, such as [Skill1 +x], [Skill2 +x], e.g., Creativity +10, UI/UX +8. Add a title banner at the top of the card and a character nameplate at the bottom. The card border should be clean and sharp, like a real collectible figurine packaging box. The background should match the profession's theme. Use warm highlights and colors that match the profession's characteristics for the color scheme.",
