    "id": "davidwuw-48",
    "prompt": "Create a high-resolution 3D render of [🥹] designed as an inflatable, puffy object. The shape should be soft, round, and air-filled — similar to a plush balloon or inflatable toy. Use a smooth matte material with subtle fabric creases and stitching to enhance the inflated effect. The overall form should be slightly irregular and softly deflated, with soft shadows and soft lighting to emphasize volume and realism. Place it on a clean, minimalist background (light gray or light blue), and the overall style should remain playful yet sculptural.",
