    "prompt": "Double exposure, Midjourney style, fused, blended, overlaid double exposure image, double exposure style. An outstanding masterpiece by Yukisakura, showcasing a wonderful double exposure composition that harmoniously interweaves the silhouette of Aragorn, son of Arathorn, with the visually striking, rugged landscapes of Middle-earth in vibrant spring. Sunlit pine forests, mountain peaks, and a lone horse crossing a trail echo outward from the textures of his form, adding layers of narrative and solitude. A beautiful tension builds as the clean, crisp monochrome background maintains sharp contrast, drawing all focus to the richly layered double exposure. It features a vibrant full-color palette inside Aragorn's silhouette, with clear, deliberate lines tracing every contour with emotional precision. (Detailed:1.45). (Detailed background:1.4).",
