    "id": "davidwuw-3",
    "prompt": "A black-and-white photo showing a blurred silhouette of a [subject] behind a frosted or translucent surface. The [part] outline is clear, pressed against the surface, creating a sharp contrast with the rest of the hazy, blurred figure. The background is a soft gray gradient tone, enhancing the mysterious and artistic atmosphere.",
