    "prompt": "Transform the image into an ancient treasure map drawn on aged parchment. The map contains detailed elements such as sailing ships on the ocean, ancient ports or castles along the coastline, dotted-line paths leading to a marked treasure location with a large \"X\", mountains, palm trees, and a decorative compass rose. The overall style is reminiscent of old pirate adventure movies.",
